{"lemma":"دَرْء","slug":"دَرْء","root":"د.ر.#","root_slug":"د-ر-_","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ر-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12351","n12352"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%A1"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12351","headword_ar":"دَرْءٌ","root":"drA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and inf. n. of 1 in senses pointed out above. (S, M, &c.) So of that verb said of a torrent. (TA.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA=y^a Als~ayolu daro'FA","text_ar":"جَا=يَ السَّيْلُ دَرْءًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duro'FA","text_ar":"دُرْءًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The torrent rushed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poured forth with vehemence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came rushing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a distant place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unknown:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA:) or the latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the torrent came from a distant land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwaAdiY duro'FA","text_ar":"الوَادِى دُرْءًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The valley flowed with the rain of another valley:"},{"kind":"text","text":"if with its own rain, you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAla ZahorFA","text_ar":"سَالَ ظَهْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, M; and the like is said in the TA in the present art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zhr","text_ar":"ظهر"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sAl","text_ar":"سال"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duro'FA","text_ar":"دُرْءًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it flowed with other than its own rain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZahorFA","text_ar":"ظَهْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", “ with its own rain. ” (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zhr","text_ar":"ظهر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Hence ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~uro'u","text_ar":"الدُّرْءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been metaphorically used by a rájiz to signify (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The flowing of water from the mouths of camels into their insides."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bending;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a crookedness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"curvity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K, TA;) in a cane, or spearshaft, and the like; (M, K;) or in a staff, and anything that is hard to straighten: (T, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duruwo'N","text_ar":"دُرُوْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqamotu daro'N fulaAnK","text_ar":"اَقَمْتُ دَرْءٌ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I rectified the crookedness and opposition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resistance, of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biy^orN *aAtu daro'K","text_ar":"بِيْرٌ ذَاتُ دَرْءٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A well having a part"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of its shaft"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"projecting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protuberant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariyqN *uw duruwo'K","text_ar":"طَرِيقٌ ذُو دُرُوْءٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A road having furrows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, * K, *) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abrupt, water-worn, ridges,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and protuberances, and the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; because it repels therewith. (Ham p. 213.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of a mountain that projects,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"juts out, from the rest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA, and Ham"},{"kind":"page_break","n":866},{"kind":"text","text":"p. 213 in explanation of the pl.,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unexpectedly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. as above. (M.) ―         -b4-  See also 1, last sentence. ―         -b5-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disobedience, and resistance, and hatred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dislike,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and crookedness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and disagreement, on the part of a wife."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA","T","S"]},{"entry_id":"n12352","headword_ar":"دُرْءٌ","root":"drA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daro'N","text_ar":"دَرْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}